textAnnotations.description:
Caganie from the Seure
aCrganics presents this blend of
hand-picked organic oolong tea with
juicy sweet peach as a classic refresher
Coiang tea is semi-oxidized-landing
somewhere between green
and black tea on
the axidation
spectrum for a
fruity, full taste.
The combination
of peach fruit flavor and oolong tea
is something you'll surely remember.
